      "Based on my web search, I found some relevant information about Devin AI and recent developments in the AI coding space, though the results don't show specific February 2025 updates. Here's what I found:\n\n## Key Findings:\n\n### **About Devin AI**\n- **Devin** is developed by **Cognition AI** and was launched in March 2024 as the world's first \"AI software engineer\"\n- Unlike traditional code assistants like GitHub Copilot, Devin can perform **end-to-end autonomous development** - from planning and coding to testing and deployment\n- It achieved a **13.86% problem-solving rate** on SWE-bench benchmark (significantly higher than GPT-4's 1.74%)\n\n### **Recent Company Developments**\nAccording to the search results:\n- **September 2025**: Cognition completed a **$400 million funding round**, reaching a **$10.2 billion valuation**\n- Major enterprise clients include **Goldman Sachs**, **Citibank**, and financial tech company **Ramp**\n- Cognition acquired assets and team from AI coding startup **Windsurf** in 2025\n\n### **Product Capabilities**\n- Full-stack development with autonomous code writing, debugging, and deployment\n- Supports multiple languages (Python, JavaScript, HTML, CSS, etc.)\n- Can learn new technologies by reading documentation and API references\n- Operates in a sandboxed environment with its own code editor, terminal, and browser\n\n### **Important Note**\nThe search results show content from **2026 dates** (appears to be a data indexing issue), but these reference events from 2024-2025. The results don't contain specific **February 2025 updates** for Devin AI.\n\n**Would you like me to search with different terms or look for more recent information about Devin's specific features or developments?**"
