um推出免费的智能代码补全神器 Windsurf Editor， 以对话方式编写完整项目代码\",\"url\":\"https://www.xmsumi.com/detail/272\"},{\"title\":\"Windsurf Wave 4版本发布，新增预览功能、支持指哪改哪\",\"url\":\"https://baijiahao.baidu.com/s?id=1825901017149709058\"},{\"title\":\"Windsurf\",\"url\":\"https://baike.sogou.com/v225290876.htm\"},{\"title\":\"AI Code\",\"url\":\"https://m.toutiao.com/article/7483235255818732032/\"}]\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"Windsurf 新版来了！Wave 6 一键部署不离IDE，网友：在Windsurf、Cursor、Cline之间选好难。\",\"url\":\"https://developer.volcengine.com/articles/7490492977564336139\"},{\"title\":\"Windsurf 又进化！Wave 5 Tab上线，打通Cascade 、终端、剪贴板\",\"url\":\"https://cloud.tencent.com/developer/article/2506869?policyId=1004\"},{\"title\":\"Windsurf 又进化！Wave 5 Tab上线，打通Cascade、终端、剪贴板，官方：打造所有人最佳编码平台\",\"url\":\"https://baijiahao.baidu.com/s?id=1827142736841181496\"},{\"title\":\"Windsurf\",\"url\":\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/Windsurf/65588540\"},{\"title\":\"Windsurf 宣布推出 Windsurf Wave 5，此次更新带来了一个全新的功能Windsurf Tab\",\"url\":\"https://sd114.wiki/8300.html\"},{\"title\":\"Claude Code 史诗级更新，AI 编程爱好者有福了！【AI 早报 2025-08-15】\",\"url\":\"https://m.bilibili.com/video/BV15pb7zYEYD/\"},{\"title\":\"Windsurf 又进化！Wave 5 Tab上线，打通Cascade 、终端、剪贴板 ...\",\"url\":\"https://cloud.tencent.cn/developer/article/2506869\"},{\"title\":\"Windsurf Wave 4版本发布：AI编程工具再升级 更智能、更高效\",\"url\":\"https://media.momodel.cn/article/%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%25A2%25A6ai%25E6%258E%25A8%25E5%2585%25A8%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%258A%25A8%25E4%25BD%259C%25E6%25A8%25A1%25E4%25BB%25BF-%25E5%258A%259F%25E8%2583%25BD%25EF%25BC%259A%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%2589%25A9%25E5%259B%25BE%25E7%2589%2587%25E5%258F%2582%25E8%2580%2583%25E8%25A7%2586/5317/latest-articles\"},{\"title\":\"Windsurf - Jimmy Song\",\"url\":\"https://jimmysong.io/ai/windsurf/\"},{\"title\":\"全新WAVES16效果器插件全套！Waves Ultimate 16 v2025.08.25 WIN&MAC\",\"url\":\"https://audio-y.com/audio-y.com/waves-ultimate-16-v2025-08-25-winampmac/\"}]\n\nBased on my web search, here's what I found about **Windsurf (Codeium) new features and updates around February 2025**:\n\n## Search Results Summary\n\nI wasn't able to find specific updates released **during** February 2025, but I found several relevant updates from the surrounding period:\n\n### Most Recent Updates Around That Time Period:\n\n**Wave 4 Release (March 5, 2025)**\nReleased just after February, Wave 4 introduced several significant features:\n- **Previews functionality** - Interactive preview allowing real-time viewing of code changes\n- **Tab to Import** - Simplifies dependency package additions by pressing Tab\n- **Cascade assistant improvements** - AI-powered suggestions for next actions\n- **Linter integration** - Real-time code quality checking\n- **Drag-and-drop file support** for multimodal inputs\n- **Model options management controls** for team/admin users\n\n**Wave 5 Release (March 20, 2025)**\nFocusing on a single major feature:\n- **Windsurf Tab integration** - Comprehensive \"Tab\" system combining:\n  - Tab-to-jump (from Wave 3)\n  - Tab-to-import (from Wave 4)\n  - Improved model and system optimizations for lower latency and higher reliability\n  - Integration with Cascade agent system\n\n**Wave 3 (Earlier in 2025)**\n- **MCP (Model Context Protocol) support**\n- **Tab-to-jump** functionality for cursor positioning\n- **Turbo mode** for automatic command execution\n\n### Important Context:\n- Windsurf uses a **\"Wave\" versioning system** for major feature releases\n- The product was **rebranded from Codeium to Windsurf** in April 2025 with a new visual identity\n- Major **Wave 13** release came much later (December 2025) with SWE-1.5 model\n\n### Note:\nNo specific updates were found for **February 2025** specifically. The closest major releases were Wave 4 (early March) and Wave 5 (late March). Windsurf appears to have released major updates in March rather than February 2025.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."
